別, 收窄返價格差距, 返返去當年KEPLER MAXWELL年代<br />\nPASCAL定價本來就已經貴左, 又玩埋公版非公定價, 白撚痴, 食開屎食慒左話返傳統做法係奇怪, 抵老黃上年LAUNCH RTX嗰陣一隻RT DLSS驚都冇, 亦唔送驚, 撚鳩班傻閪買, 極高炒價但花MON<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d388c64e3c51e528d5813f23461698e3e53062b","tid":1061874,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"773a8e6988ee6b266ac2e353514d747a86823c8d","tid":1061874,"uid":80473,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"硬件台狀況:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQdg6dJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQdg6dJ.gif&h=5dd30c28&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:01:48.000Z","msg":"去睇一轉時事台，個戰況就好似8人打stage mode邪鬼嗰陣咁撚柒亂"},{"pid":"12eb87d50ba3cf37e8e44c4cdbfa2df5f4197c83","tid":1061874,"uid":124785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"389377b6016f33d963d5386308876ebf40e8ebc6","tid":1061874,"uid":61763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"1070苦主行預設2000MHZ都花MON<br />\n1660輕鬆超到2400~2500<br />\n公平咩, D9VVR我屌你老母呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD9TCB USER<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:28:44.000Z","msg":"1700 MHz 上到 2400 ??<br />\n認真咩? <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/24970/asus-geforce-gtx-1660/?fbclid=IwAR0nS9rvgqRVUbWd3OtdZDiETCYZ38proS3kmZMcOYgZwH-mL8g_NZDXrfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F24970%2Fasus-geforce-gtx-1660%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0nS9rvgqRVUbWd3OtdZDiETCYZ38proS3kmZMcOYgZwH-mL8g_NZDXrfw&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=42cff256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/24970/asus-geforce-gtx-1660/?fbclid=IwAR0nS9rvgqRVUbWd3OtdZDiETCYZ38proS3kmZMcOYgZwH-mL8g_NZDXrfw</a><br />\n佢地都淨係上到1900 MHz"},{"pid":"d52daf123876123afd525db1f0b37c7a88cd275b","tid":1061874,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1